data.description: Short Sale - Stunning 2-Story, 5 Bedroom 2.5 Bath Plus .25 Acre Lot In Land O Lakes/Wesley Chapel Area. This Newer Home Is A Great Value In The Enclave Community. Conveniently Located Off Of Sr 54 With An Easy Drive To Usf, I75 And Wire Grass Shopping, This Community Is A Must See. With More Than 2100Sf Of Living Space And 5 Bedrooms This Home Is Perfect For A Large Family. There Are 4 Bedrooms On The Second Level And A Guest Bedroom On The First Floor. Features Include: Upgraded Maple Cabinets, Vinyl Insulated Tilt-In Windows And French Doors, Arches Throughout, Large Covered Patio For Entertaining. Does Need Some Work But You Can Build Up Equity Fast With This Property. Low Monthly Hoa Of $23. No Cdd. The Spacious Island Kitchen Overlooks The Family Room So You Can Watch The Kids While Preparing Meals. Entertaining For Large Gatherings Is Fun And Easy With The Great Room And Formal Dining Room. There Is A Powder Room Located Down As Well. The Upstairs Master Retreat Has A Large Walk-In Closet And Separate Tub And Shower. The Corner Lot Is Fenced With Room For A Boat Or Rv. Home Is Sold As-Is With Right To Inspect. See Attachments In Mls.
